w.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bf/Harvest-Basil-Step-11.jpg/v4-460px-Harvest-Basil-Step-11.jpg", "vid": null}, "12": {"text": "Keep fresh basil in water.", "img": "https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/11/Preserve-Basil-Step-3.jpg/v4-460px-Preserve-Basil-Step-3.jpg", "vid": null}, "13": {"text": "Make \u201cbasil cubes.", "img": "https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c1/Harvest-Basil-Step-13.jpg/v4-460px-Harvest-Basil-Step-13.jpg", "vid": null}}